QUALIFICATION: Dr S. Bílý, National Museum Prague (in press), proposes that Anthaxia novaehollandiae Obenberger, 1928 be synonymized under Anthaxia (Haplanthaxia) splendida Chevrolat, 1837, a species from southern Africa. This will eliminate the species and the genus from the Australian fauna, long suspected of being in error
